Brigands' loot
The loot taken by the brigands must be returned to the village!
#subobj  1
Finding the coffer
The coffer with the loot stands in the middle of the Brigands' camp located in the northern part of the Foothills. Both the approaches to the camp and the coffer are guarded very well
#subobj  2
Take the loot
To take the loot, you must open the coffer.
